          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Remove Extraneous Measures that Obstruct Value and Efficiency Act or the REMOVE Act</b></p> <p>This bill specifies factors that the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services must consider when&nbsp;(1) removing a quality measure from certain Medicare payment systems,&nbsp;or (2) selecting or updating quality measures to use under Medicare.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-12-11T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
